title: Lovely 2B/1B Duplex Located Near Willow Glen!
posting_body: ['This charming duplex is nestled in the perfect location!', 'You will be minutes to Downtown Willow Glen and Downtown Campbell.', 'Living here will provide you with a convenient commute opportunity with access to hwy 87 and 280.', 'You do not want to miss the opportunity to be the first resident in this beautiful duplex.', 'Home Details:', '2-Bedrooms', '1 Bathroom', 'Bright Living Room', 'Hardwood flooring throughout living space and bedrooms', '(2) Two Linen closet spaces in hall', 'Bathroom features plank flooring', 'Tub/Shower combination', 'Eat in Kitchen', 'Electric Range', 'Dishwasher', 'Refrigerator', 'Washer & Dryer', 'Street Parking only – no garage access', 'No Smoking', 'Small Pets ok – Dogs $100 a month, Cats $50 a month', '1 Year Lease Minimum', 'The resident is responsible for water, trash, sewer, PG&E', 'Neighborhood:', '1.5 Miles to Almaden Ranch Plaza', '1.5 Miles to Almaden Plaza', 'Walgreens, Dunkin Donuts, F45 Fitness all a block away', 'Schools:', 'Schallenberger Elementary', 'Willow Glen Middle School', 'Willow Glen High School', '*applicants to confirm eligibility*', '-', 'Apply online today: <URL>', '- Non-Refundable $45 application fee per person.', '*Credit Screening Required*', '- Applicant must submit proof of gross income (2.5x monthly rent)', '- Deposit is equal to one month’s rent on approved credit', 'To schedule a private tour please contact Forbes Group at', 'show contact info', 'or email leasing @ <URL>', 'All the Best,', 'Forbes Group Property Management', '<URL>']
